-- MOVES-FTI Consulting names Nigel Churton as GRIP senior adviser
-- By Rama Venkat Raman in Bangalore
-- Mon Sep 29, 2014 06:15AM EDT
-- None



Sept 29 (Reuters) - Business advisory firm FTI Consulting Inc <FCN.N> appointed Nigel Churton as international senior adviser in its global risk and investigations practice (GRIP).

Churton will be based in London and will provide strategic guidance to clients across Europe, the Middle East and Africa (EMEA). He previously served as a vice-chairman at global risk consultancy firm Control Risks Group Ltd.